def repositionGlyph(glyph,transformX,transformY):
glyph.layers[0].applyTransform(( 1.0, # x scale factor 0.0, # x skew factor 0.0, # y skew factor 1.0, # y scale factor transformX, # x position transformY # y position )) glyph.layers[0].LSB = (1200-glyph.layers[0].bounds.size.width) / 2 glyph.layers[0].width = 1200

glyph.layers[0].applyTransform(( scaleFactor, # x scale factor 0.0, # x skew factor 0.0, # y skew factor scaleFactor, # y scale factor 0.0, # x position 0.0 # y position ))
